x4freetext: The working electron beam current was 0.15 uA, beam
In this regime accelerator worked 10000 hours.
Cooling time from bremsstrahlung intensive experiments
to present radiation measurement is 35 years.
A tantalum plate of 0.3 mm in thickness was set at the
output of the accelerator on the electron beam way.
<sigma>:average cross section between Eth and E0 (BRS)
sigmaq: cross section per equivalent quantum (BRA)
The typical statistical errors deduced from the areas
of the gamma lines were less then 3-5%.
